      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear what you're saying about institutions, but it feels like you're basically saying nationalism is always a net negative. aren't you just ignoring the fact that most successful states in history relied on some level of national spirit to function? it seems like you've already decided it's a bad thing before even looking at the benefits.",
